_:N5870aa7d51cb43639f4b3899f7797406 <http://schema.org/description> "The Office for the Pay Review Bodies provides an independent secretariat to 8 Pay Review Bodies which make recommendations impacting 2.5 million workers – around 45% of public sector staff – and a pay bill of £100 billion. OPRB is part of the Department for Business and Trade ." .
